rComments: The best professor of my life. It was an honor to have had him as my professor. Congrats, Professor Vanka. You are the best! So sad you have retired!
Best Prof I have taken a class from in UIUC. One of the reasons I am still in Grad School.
The best professor of my life. Too bad he has retired.

He is a great lecturer who is easy to follow and who stresses the main concepts in his lectures. He can be defined as a great professor because his tests and quizzes are challenging yet if you go to lecture and do the relatively easy book problems, you should get an A. Also heard good things about ME 320. He doesn't accept BS though so don't try.
